---
title: Chicken Penne with Spinach-Tomato Cream Sauce
description: If it ain't broke, don't fix it. That's what we have to say about the tried-and-true combination of spinach and sun-dried tomatoes. Folded into a creamy tomato sauce with juicy bites of chicken and ample parmesan, this is a bowl of pasta to curl up with.
